msgstr "写入数据"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/getting-started-dev-services.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To use the new entity, update the `hello` method to start writing some data."
msgstr "要使用这个新实体，请更新 `hello` 方法，开始写入一些数据。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/getting-started-dev-services.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Change the method to the following:"
msgstr "将该方法修改为以下内容："

